collections.name: Wonderful World NFT
collections.description:
"Wonderful World" is an exclusive NFT collection featuring unique digital artworks representing 194 countries. Each piece showcases an iconic landmark, a character, and an animal symbolizing the nation's heritage, all in vibrant neon colors with the country's flag and name.

The collection offers three editions:

Standard NFTs – colorful representations available in wider quantities.
Gold Editions – limited to only 20 pieces per country worldwide, offering premium, luxurious designs.
Diamond Editions – ultra-rare, with only one NFT per country, featuring exclusive, high-end visuals for true collectors.

Every day, an NFT collection from one country will be released.

collections.name: Lighthouse, Suva: Golden Hour
collections.description: "Lighthouse, Suva: Golden Hour" is a collection of 62 unique (1/1) digital artworks capturing the unforgettable feeling of looking back and watching the Lighthouse Surf break continuing to crank after a perfect late afternoon session. Each piece is a unique impression of the same image that combines the iconic lighthouse, a perfectly peeling wave, a spectacular Suva sunset, and the familiar view from the back of a departing boat.  These images are more than just pictures; they're visual memories, imbued with the nostalgia and satisfaction of a session well-surfed.  Each variation subtly reflects the changing light, swell, and atmosphere of this special place, offering a unique connection to the magic of the Lighthouse.
